<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>验证您的邮箱地址</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .message {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .fallback-link {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .fallback-link strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .warning {
            color: #dc3545;
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>📧 验证您的邮箱地址</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">你好 {{username}}，</p>
            <p class="message">
                感谢您注册 My-KM 个人知识管理系统！<br>
                请点击下方按钮验证您的邮箱地址：
            </p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{verifyUrl}}" class="button">验证邮箱</a>
            </div>
            <p class="message">如果按钮无法点击，请复制以下链接到浏览器地址栏：</p>
            <div class="fallback-link">
                <strong>验证链接：</strong>
                {{verifyUrl}}
            </div>
            <div class="warning">
                <strong>⚠️ 重要提示：</strong><br>
                此链接将在 24 小时后过期。请尽快完成验证。
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>如果您没有注册 My-KM 账户，请忽略此邮件。</p>
            <p>© {{year}} My-KM. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
